The paper deals with power control and precoding design in a cell-free massive MIMO network, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and game theory (cs.GT). However, since the focus is on optimizing energy efficiency, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
